@nationalism
on-arrival: {! globalThis.prepareDdpCongress(Q); !}

= Nationalism

Current adopted position: [+ ddp_nationalism_position : ddp_nationalism_position +]

Oppose Extreme Nationalism: [+ ddp_congress_nationalism_oppose_extreme_nationalism_debug +]
Supports: left progressive; neutral: left liberal; opposes: laborist, left bourgeois, regionalist.

Support Liberal Civic Nationalism: [+ ddp_congress_nationalism_liberal_civic_nationalism_debug +]
Supports: left liberal; neutral: left progressive, laborist, left bourgeois; opposes: regionalist.

Use Nationalism for Political Benefit: [+ ddp_congress_nationalism_political_benefit_nationalism_debug +]
Supports: left bourgeois, regionalist; neutral: laborist, left liberal; opposes: left progressive.

Support German Racial Nationalism: [+ ddp_congress_nationalism_german_racial_nationalism_debug +]
Supports: regionalist; neutral: left bourgeois; opposes: left progressive, laborist, left liberal.

[? if ddp_congress_nationalism_selectable = 0: No alternative position has majority support at this congress. ?]

- @nationalism_oppose_extreme_nationalism: Adopt: Oppose Extreme Nationalism
- @nationalism_liberal_civic_nationalism: Adopt: Support Liberal Civic Nationalism
- @nationalism_political_benefit_nationalism: Adopt: Use Nationalism for Political Benefit
- @nationalism_german_racial_nationalism: Adopt: Support German Racial Nationalism
- @nationalism_continue: Continue

@nationalism_oppose_extreme_nationalism
