= Economics

Current adopted position: [+ ddp_economics_position : ddp_economics_position +]

Support Interventionist Economics: [+ ddp_congress_economic_interventionist_economics_debug +]
Supports: left progressive, laborist; neutral: left liberal; opposes: left bourgeois, regionalist.

Support a Social Liberal Economy: [+ ddp_congress_economic_social_liberal_economy_debug +]
