@leader
on-arrival: {! globalThis.prepareDdpCongress(Q); !}

= Leader

Current adopted position: [+ ddp_leader : ddp_leader_position +]

Anton Erkelenz: [+ ddp_congress_leader_anton_erkelenz_debug +]
Supports: left progressive, laborist; neutral: none; opposes: left liberal, left bourgeois, regionalist.

Theodor Heuss: [+ ddp_congress_leader_theodor_heuss_debug +]
Supports: left progressive, left liberal; neutral: laborist; opposes: left bourgeois, regionalist.

Theodor Maier: [+ ddp_congress_leader_theodor_maier_debug +]
Supports: left liberal, left bourgeois; neutral: none; opposes: left progressive, laborist, regionalist.

Otto Fischbeck: [+ ddp_congress_leader_otto_fischbeck_debug +]
Supports: regionalist; neutral: left bourgeois; opposes: left progressive, laborist, left liberal.

Erich Koch-Weser: [+ ddp_congress_leader_erich_koch_weser_debug +]
Supports: left bourgeois, left liberal; neutral: left progressive, laborist, regionalist; opposes: none.

Hermann Dietrich: [+ ddp_congress_leader_hermann_dietrich_debug +]
Supports: regionalist, left bourgeois; neutral: none; opposes: left progressive, laborist, left liberal.

